The plugin comes with a controller for dynamic access control. Its called [controller:access] and you can use it as
soon as you let one of your roles access it.

h3. Access TagLib
Included in the plugin is a taglib containing some useful tags. Example:
{code}
<access:hasAccess controller="access">
  <li class="controller"><g:link controller="access"><g:message code="generic.access"/></g:link></li>
</access:hasAccess>
{code}